# lsearch-index - Index Knowledge Base

Manually trigger indexing of configured knowledge base paths.

## Usage

```
/lsearch-index [path]
```

## Arguments

- `path` (optional): Specific path to index. If not provided, indexes all configured paths.

## Examples

```bash
# Index all configured paths
/lsearch-index

# Index specific directory
/lsearch-index ./docs

# Index specific file
/lsearch-index ./README.md
```
